text: The Volkswagen Tiguan is an SUV produced by Volkswagen since 2007. == Engines == * 1.4 TSI 110 kW (150 hp) * 2.0 TSI 125 kW (170 hp) and 147 kW (200 hp) * 2.0 TDI 100 kW (136 hp), 103 kW (140 hp), 120 kW (163 hp) and 125 kW (170 hp) Tiguan Category:Sport utility vehicles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles
title: Volkswagen Tiguan
